  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      All patients with non variceal bleed who are admitted under the Department of Hepatology at
      Institute of Liver and Biliary Sciences, who meet the inclusion criteria and who provide
      informed consent.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
